With nearly 2,500 graduate students, SIUE is committed to educating a distinguished and diverse cohort of master's and doctoral students. The graduate programs emphasize scholarly activity and practice. Eighty percent of full-time instructional faculty have a terminal degree for their discipline. Students learn in modern facilities, including state-of-the-art labs and inspiring studios and performance spaces.
